9nlgkGDR-Jg.title: The Prismatic World Tour Live
9nlgkGDR-Jg.description:
Pre-order your copy today at http://katyperry.com/PWTL 

On October 30, 2015, Katy releases her concert film “The Prismatic World Tour Live”on DVD, Blu-ray and digital download. 
 
“The Prismatic World Tour Live” captures the excitement of the live Katy Perry extravaganza that Rolling Stone hailed as "a show to damage retinas and blow minds…never less than uproariously entertaining." Presented in seven thematic acts, it is enhanced by flawless production and innovative staging, which spanned the entire length of the arena floor. All formats of “The Prismatic World Tour Live” also include 30 minutes of exclusive extras.
 
In this no-holds-barred full-length live spectacular, Katy performs the global smash hits “Roar,” “Firework,” “I Kissed A Girl,” “Dark Horse,” “California Gurls” and “Hot N Cold” along with other Billboard Hot 100 No. 1 singles and fan favorites. The concert film is a visually stunning production, complete with eye-popping theatrics, daring acrobatics, exotic costumes and much more.
 
The Prismatic World Tour began in May 2014 and will conclude in October 2015. After a total of 151 shows over 6 legs on 5 continents, Katy will have played to 2 million people with this audiovisual spectacular.
